'''第43届[[全美音乐奖|全美音乐奖]]'''（{{lang-en|43rd Annual American Music Awards}}）于2015年11月22日在美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]{{le|微软剧院|Microsoft Theater}}举行<ref name="noms">{{cite web | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6723082/american-music-awards-2015-nominees | title=2015 American Music Awards: Taylor Swift Leads Nominations | publisher=Billboard | work=Prometheus Global Media | date=2015-10-13 | accessdate=2015-10-13 | archive-date=2019-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223173556/https://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6723082/american-music-awards-2015-nominees | dead-url=no }}</ref>。典礼由[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]转播，[[詹妮弗·洛佩兹|詹妮弗·洛佩兹]]主持<ref name="Lopez to host">{{cite web|author=Associated Press|title=Jennifer Lopez to host the 2015 American Music Awards|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/jennifer-lopez-to-host-the-2015-american-music-awards/|website=cbsnews.com|publisher=CBS Interactive Inc.|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-12-05|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608024230/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/jennifer-lopez-to-host-the-2015-american-music-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]凭借三项大奖成为当晚最大赢家，也是入圍最多的歌手<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6770317/american-music-awards-2015-winners-list-amas?utm_source=pushdown&utm_medium=www&utm_campaign=grammys | title=American Music Awards 2015: Check Out All the Winners Here | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=Billboard | date=2015-11-22 | accessdate=2015-11-23 | archive-date=2015-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124125619/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6770317/american-music-awards-2015-winners-list-amas?utm_source=pushdown&utm_medium=www&utm_campaign=grammys | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[杰瑞德·莱托|杰瑞德·莱托]]为[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|2015年11月巴黎袭击事件]]致以哀悼，之后由[[席琳·迪翁|席琳·迪翁]]奉献致敬表演<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6770354/jared-leto-2015-american-music-awards-immigrants-speech | title=Jared Leto at the 2015 American Music Awards: 'Many of Us Here Are the Sons and Daughters of Immigrants' | publisher=Prometheus Global Media | work=Billboard | date=2015-11-22 | accessdate=2015-11-23 | archive-date=2015-11-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125164048/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6770354/jared-leto-2015-american-music-awards-immigrants-speech | dead-url=no }}</ref>。共有1098万美国观众收看了电视转播<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/11/23/tv-ratings-sunday-nov-22-2015/ |title=TV Ratings Sunday: American Music Awards down vs. 2014, ‘Good Wife’ slips below 1.0 |accessdate=2015-12-05 |archive-date=2015-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206070517/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/11/23/tv-ratings-sunday-nov-22-2015/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

